"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:10:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:43:32.000Z","msg":"係，五年前一早講咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f738fa6880dafabcafd078276c75c245f859327","tid":1206480,"uid":248335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ff62411b4269b61d78b86ce774a19f126099b7","tid":1206480,"uid":131621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:47:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee4dc21f30ec0b1a23891eac1ec673a2e4274b8b","tid":1206480,"uid":82002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2842ee5a33e3a727f6edc07d65785ed6b3d32596","tid":1206480,"uid":23573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8068e2c9579d58cc1fbe74bd52e2bc1f95f18172","tid":1206480,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/un1GB22.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fun1GB22.png&h=9f65aace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑色係群眾，目前Harcourt，添美係最多人。<br />\n添華道，龍和道人群開始被扯去以上兩個地方，<br />\n後join巴打要補充人手既話可以去添華，<br />\n如果警察係中環同埋添華龍華交界，造突破口的話<br />\n唔夠人頂就好容易四散<br />\n<br />\n紅色係持盾警察，雖然全部有棍，但唔係清場部隊。<br />\n同人群距離最近，但行動力唔高，<br />\n睇個款係其他區調過黎做樣居多，<br />\nSupport既兵力目前集結分域碼頭同中環碼頭，<br />\n隨時可以增援。<br />\n有部分持盾警察用言語同手勢挑釁群眾。<br />\n<br />\n橙色係精銳清場部隊，暫時未有動靜，<br />\n直接面對群眾既數目唔多，<br />\n但留意到大部分目前都屯係添華道同立法會東翼門口，<br />\n預計係為攻擊衝擊立法會群眾做準備。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><strong>唔該後join巴打帶長遮，索帶，口罩，眼罩，現場物資不足</strong></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n隨時再update"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:41:22.000Z","msg":"警察應該有能力先從龍匯道入添美道<br />\n打斷南北人群，防止夏愨嘅人支援龍和道<br />\n然後加上碼頭方向嘅增援包夾龍和道嘅人<br />\n警察對夏愨同添美道嘅優先度應該係最低"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:47:26.000Z","msg":"其實警察兩個方法都有道理，因為添華係成個包圍圈貫通南北兩面既命脈<br />\n<br />\n1. 速龍經龍匯入添美迴旋，分割兩邊，清龍和添華場<br />\n<br />\n2. 速龍經添華出龍和，同分域碼頭兵力兩邊包抄，收復迴旋處同半條添美<br />\n<br />\n因為目前harcourt 添美依家人數大致足夠，<br />\n佢地唔會選擇用黎突破<br />\n<br />\n所以，添華同添美迴旋先係群眾既軟肋"},{"pid":"893dd781318107381c2e0aa62d803c181d9c56a0","tid":1206480,"uid":27411,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791af5b404af4963d592c11cb638102e05c96721","tid":1206480,"uid":119996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b439c09acdfd3b93eaf94af1137259fe3f4f7f4","tid":1206480,"uid":6435,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:16:34.000Z","msg":"警犬對添華同龍和睇得咁重一定有料到<br />\n尤其是佢地每次都必須要搶返龍和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警犬唔會做無戰術意義既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:48:16.000Z","msg":"咁點解呢<br />\n花生友好奇一問"},{"pid":"40d45da575007940cd67b3e9afe7247e016816f8","tid":1206480,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:49:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"37aa429e1e0dda446a3627bc89ea4923685299ae","tid":1206480,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:50:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb8da85c45a71199a6da6a0d26d4cecacb38e1cb","tid":1206480,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3145ed23fb22ab9710fd4037ae3417eda38bd59e","tid":1206480,"uid":194298,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:23:04.000Z","msg":"警犬要補給立會，一定會取回龍和"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:50:37.000Z","msg":"肯定大把秘道，唔使擔心"},{"pid":"9eeab29c190e21317d2cfb135d0827da571dce4b","tid":1206480,"uid":131040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:50:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a209e89381db4a4b1f513eb51b45132435427572","tid":1206480,"uid":162316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:50:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33a60b7285c429119