e":"2019-06-12T04:06:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e70e8572be6332ca02ab08d325677d5465f8f60","tid":1206480,"uid":81079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:16:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38dea865a57afde91debc3e37df1c892d29a3dbc","tid":1206480,"uid":188607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9788f56a9a7f5103a2b4d20d3188f214e369e1b","tid":1206480,"uid":199882,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:25:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想去又未去嘅朋友：<br />\n林鄭送終會未取消，取消嘅係另外早上八點嘅會，呢個係出fake new既仆街政府<br />\n<br />\n唔付出人力都可以付出物力，前線缺大量長傘、毛巾、眼罩、索帶、生理鹽水、保鮮紙（用黎保護身體）<br />\n<br />\n就算不了，但至少你可以share呢段訊息</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:18:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53de175d6d6292761aacd0dd2a41434b1e62761d","tid":1206480,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:21:16.000Z","msg":"有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57a1a3fc6e6f02e5aa4a887e91a006bd35cd583","tid":1206480,"uid":218181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:24:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2752d6449f18b334673b778016b7787eef65356","tid":1206480,"uid":23573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08407cfff856e9814684a166c940964b9ac1816a","tid":1206480,"uid":121324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ToUXmd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ToUXmd.png&h=79fe37b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n估計警方進攻路線，<br />\n添華道斷南北關鍵，摩天輪可落可唔落，個邊示威者連到氣都弱<br />\n紅色負責小量兵員block，橙色精兵郁手<br />\n孤立龍和道，再由添華道切割龍和道"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T04:24:25.000Z","msg":"難題係即使估到警犬想點<br />\n龍和同添華真係好難守<br />\n特別係龍和，雨革已經體驗過速龍 係龍和快速推進有幾麻煩<br />\n時間一拖得耐 龍和好易唔夠人<br />\n我唯一諗到嘅係搵方法威脅警犬係分域嘅大本營<br />\n例如灣仔方向令警犬要分心分人手處理<br />\n咁嘅話夏慤有機會可以保持經添美支援龍和"},{"pid":"38d08c180416069f4e31c7